### PetClinic Visits API - Sample Requests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7224

@petId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@vetId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@visitId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Schedule a Visit
POST {{baseUrl}}/visits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": "{{petId}}",
  "vetId": "{{vetId}}",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "reason": "Annual checkup",
  "notes": null
}

### Get Visit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}

### Get Visits by Pet
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits?petId={{petId}}

### Get Visits by Vet on a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits?vetId={{vetId}}&date=2026-04-01

### Get Scheduled Visits
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits?status=Scheduled

### Update Visit
PUT {{baseUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-04-01T11:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "reason": "Annual checkup and vaccination",
  "notes": "Bring previous records"
}

### Cancel Visit
POST {{baseUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Owner requested cancellation"
}

### Complete Visit
POST {{baseUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}/complete

### Delete Visit
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}
